query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total,
  SUM(CASE WHEN latitude IS NULL OR latitude = '' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as null_lat,
  SUM(CASE WHEN longitude IS NULL OR longitude = '' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as null_lng
FROM projects WHERE documentId = 1;
